---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Operating Systems · Virtual Labs · AquinTutor" description="Interactive operating-systems virtual lab: CPU scheduling, page replacement, disk scheduling, Banker's deadlock avoidance, memory allocation and producer-consumer semaphores with genuine computation.">
