                    <button class="btn amber full" id="bkTest">Test request</button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="log" id="bkLog"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="sec quiz"><div class="quiz" data-quiz="4"></div></div>

          <div class="sec ref"><ul class="refs">
            <li><b>Dijkstra, E. W.</b> &mdash; EWD108: Een algorithme ter voorkoming van de dodelijke omarming (the Banker's algorithm), 1965.</li>
            <li><b>Silberschatz, Galvin &amp; Gagne</b> &mdash; Operating System Concepts, 10th ed., Ch. 8 (Deadlocks). Wiley.</li>
            <li><b>Virtual Labs (IIT)</b> &mdash; Operating Systems: Deadlock Avoidance, cse02.vlabs.ac.in.</li>
          </ul></div>
